{"tid":1994645,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"梁美芬：港台有節目讓年青人分享為何變成「暴徒」，內容偏激，對思想沒有「免疫力」的年輕人相當「入腦」","createTime":"2020-04-29T15:24:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-29T15:33:49.000Z","uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"4b024cdfb379bf8be20309bb516d65649a47b72d","tid":1994645,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T15:24:09.000Z","msg":"立法會繼續審議財政預算案，進入全體委員會階段。經民聯議員梁美芬批評，<span style=\"color: red;\">香港電台節目偏激及偏頗，對思想沒有「免疫力」的年輕人相當「入腦」</span>。<br />\n<br />\n梁美芬指，<span style=\"color: red;\">有周末下午的節目內容偏激，亦有節目讓年青人分享為何變成暴徒，但聽不到平衡意見</span>，認為如果港台屬香港人的電台，就要反映香港人真正的聲音。她表示，港台收受公帑運作，應該受立法會議員監督，又指與廣播處長梁家榮相識多年，希望梁家榮要細聽港台不同節目，以防節目偏頗。<br />\n<br />\n梁美芬又指，香港很多人希望重拾法治社會，回復安全及和平，屬香港人的真正聲音，但香港出現「攬炒派」，又指公民黨曾表明一旦民主派於立法會取得過半議席，就會否決財政預算案。<br />\n<br />\n公民黨陳淑莊就指， <span style=\"color: red;\">真正香港人聲音，已經於區議會選舉反映，但政府充耳不聞</span>，區議員不能於區議會討論警方執法，受民政專員限制，質疑政府才是「真攬炒」。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1523435-20200429.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1523435-20200429.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=JNpWH9nW0yy7OMfwbmfjwxBk8ry%2Bv12G5j1RUyKX8i0%3D&h=97978ee5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1523435-20200429.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=cdd93571\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1523435-20200429.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"f7cd75cbab79936c7c3e1b3288173716cf47796e","tid":1994645,"uid":281020,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T15:25:04.000Z","msg":"港台播狗訊你又唔講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a1774297111df889fe990a1a6f5c4a9bfe81145","tid":1994645,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T15:27:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea06ea2d2a1e8600456998798167053dfe457fee","tid":1994645,"uid":187957,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T15:30:19.000Z","msg":"回帶先！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n郭家麒解釋梁美芬教授憲法，又懂得捉老鼠，本領很高，擔任立法會法律顧問會浪費她的才能。"},{"pid":"e6c8f1c8334ecf9150e281708ee34241b58d62a4","tid":1994645,"uid":121197,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T15:33:03.000Z","msg":"藍絲見到消息就鳩廣傳出去<br />\n年青人就先質疑後思考<br />\n邊面對消息免疫力低啲？"},{"pid":"293d4976848673eb433cc36aab3c57abfe29aad6","tid":1994645,"uid":264245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T15:33:49.000Z","msg":"睇完警訊d情操先咁高尚既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}